where \(N\) is the number of training samples and \(\bm{X}_{i},\bm{y}_{i}\) are query and response sequences sampled from any conversational-style data, respectively. \(\theta^{\prime}_{(\cdot)}\) is the updated weight in full fine-tuning or the

